OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FCovid closures still       
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Faffecting 400 million      
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fpupils - Unicef            
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Schools in 23 countries, with 405      
OL,6, million pupils, are still partially or 
OL,7, fully closed because of Covid, the     
OL,8, United Nations Children's Fund says.   
OL,10,FThe charity, Unicef, estimates 147     
OL,11,Fmillion children have missed at least  
OL,12,Fhalf of their in-person schooling.     
OL,14,FSome vulnerable children, especially   
OL,15,Fgirls, have not returned to those      
OL,16,Fschools that have reopened.            
OL,18,FUnicef executive director Catherine    
OL,19,FRussell says children are "the hidden  
OL,20,Fcasualties of the pandemic".           
